name: Nut Quest
description: My first Jam game! Woo! In this game there is Only One enemy, Only One objective, Only One Attack, Only One room. Good luck, hope you enjoy the demo I have created over the past 2 days. All code and (unfortunately) graphics were made by me. The sound effects were generated using BFXR and the music was provided free by Juhani Junkala.
